translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  12,96,"Ke kaloku ukufika komphathi weendaba ezivuyisayo wajula (ihempe) phezu kobuso bakhe, wabona ngokucacileyo. Wathi: “Anditshongo na kuni ukuba ndazi endikwaziyo kuAllâh eningakwaziyo nina.”"
  12,97,"Bathi bona: “O tata wethu! Sicelele itarhu (kuAllâh) ngezono zethu inene thina besingaboni.”"
  12,98,"Wathi yena: “Ndiya kunicelela itarhu eNkosini yam, inene Yona Yodwa nguMxoleli, uSozinceba.”"
  12,99,"Bathi bakufika phambi koYûsuf, wawolana nabazali bakhe, wathi: “Ngenani eYiputa ngoxolo, ukuba uAllâh Uyathanda.”"
  12,100,"Ke kaloku wabaphakamisela abazali bakhe etroneni, bawa baqubuda phambi kwakhe. Wathi yena: “O tata! Le yintsingiselo yephupha lam langaphambili! INkosi yam Ilenze lazaliseka! Inene Yona Yayisoloko Ilungile kum, ukundikhuphakwaYo entolongweni,Yanizisa apha, Inikhupha kubomi bokuhamba nihlala entlango, emva kokuba uShaytân ehlwayele ubutshaba phakathi kwam nabantakwethu. Inene iNkosi yam InobuBele neMfesane kulowo Imthandileyo. Inene Yona Yiyo Yodwa EnguSolwazi, uSobulumko.”"
  12,101,"“Nkosi yam! Wena inene Undiphe ubunganga Wandifundisa nokutolika amaphupha (Wena) Mdali wamazulu nomhlaba. UnguMlondolozi wam Wena kweli hlabathi nakwelizayo. Ndenze mna ndife ndiliMuslim, Undimanye namalungisa.”"
  12,102,"Ezo ziindaba zokungabonwayo eSizityhila kuwe (Muhammad). Wena wawungekho kunye nabo xa babequlunqa bebodwa, naxa babesenza iyelenqe (labo)"
  12,103,Ke kaloku uninzi lwabantu aluyi kukholwa enokuba oko ungakulangazelela ngenkuthalo engakanani na